<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .error-container {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8d7da 0%, #f5c6cb 100%);
            border: 2px solid #dc3545;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .error-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .attempt-counter {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .progress-bar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 20px;
            background: #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #dc3545, #c82333);
            width: <%= (attempt / maxAttempts) * 100 %>%;
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }
        .error-details {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #dc3545;
            font-family: monospace;
        }
        .success-preview {
            background: #d4edda;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #155724;
        }
        .retry-info {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #856404;
            text-align: left;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-icon">🔄💥</div>
        <h1><%= title %></h1>
        <p>This endpoint fails the first <%= maxAttempts %> requests, then succeeds. Perfect for testing retry logic!</p>
        
        <div class="attempt-counter">
            <h3>Attempt Progress</h3>
            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
                <span><strong>Current Attempt:</strong> <%= attempt %> of <%= maxAttempts %></span>
                <span style="color: <%= willSucceed ? '#28a745' : '#dc3545' %>; font-weight: bold;">
                    <%= willSucceed ? '✅ Will succeed next time!' : '❌ Will fail' %>
                </span>
            </div>
            <div class="progress-bar">
                <div class="progress-fill"></div>
            </div>
            <small style="color: #6c757d;">
                <%= maxAttempts - attempt %> more failure(s) before success
            </small>
        </div>
        
        <div class="error-details">
            <h3>Current Error Details</h3>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Status Code:</span>
                <span class="detail-value"><%= errorStatus %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Error Message:</span>
                <span class="detail-value"><%= errorMessage %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Attempt Number:</span>
                <span class="detail-value"><%= attempt %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Max Attempts:</span>
                <span class="detail-value"><%= maxAttempts %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Timestamp:</span>
                <span class="detail-value"><%= new Date().toISOString() %></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <% if (willSucceed) { %>
        <div class="success-preview">
            <h4>🎉 Next Request Will Succeed!</h4>
            <p>The next request to this endpoint will return a successful response. This tests whether your retry logic works correctly.</p>
        </div>
        <% } %>
        
        <div class="retry-info">
            <h4>🔄 Retry Testing Information</h4>
            <p><strong>How this endpoint works:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Fails the first <strong><%= maxAttempts %></strong> requests with different error types</li>
                <li>Succeeds on request <strong><%= maxAttempts + 1 %></strong> and beyond</li>
                <li>Tracks attempts per client (IP + User-Agent)</li>
                <li>Resets counter after successful response</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p><strong>CLI Testing:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Use <code>--retry <%= maxAttempts + 1 %></code> to ensure success</li>
                <li>Test with fewer retries to verify failure handling</li>
                <li>Use in batch processing to test error continuation</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p><strong>Reset Counter:</strong> POST to <code>/error/flaky/reset</code> to reset all counters</p>
        </div>
        
        <p style="color: #6c757d; font-style: italic; margin-top: 30px;">
            This is attempt <%= attempt %> of <%= maxAttempts %>. 
            <%= willSucceed ? 'The next request will succeed!' : 'Keep trying!' %>
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>